### IPPC ePhyto Hub Delivery Status

The phytosanitary certificate has been transmitted to the IPPC ePhyto Hub. Click **Check Status** to query the Hub — the certificate shows as `PendingDelivery` until the importing country's NPPO downloads it, then `Delivered`, which completes this step.

- **Reference Number**: `{{ .reference_number }}`
- **Certificate Number**: `{{ .certificate_id }}`
{{ with .ephyto }}- **Hub Tracking Number**: `{{ .tracking_number }}`
{{ if .tracking_info }}- **Current Status**: `{{ .tracking_info }}`
{{ end }}{{ if .error }}
> {{ .error }}
{{ end }}{{ end }}
_Click **Check Status** to refresh._
